MOST IMMEDIATE
No. 1/34/2/2005-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 11th August, 2005
20 Sravana, 1927 (S)
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 10th August,
2005 : -
i)
Shri Jagdish Tytler relinquished the charge of the office of Minister
of State (Independent Charge) for Overseas Indian Affairs, and
ii)
The Prime Minister assumed the charge of the office of Minister of
Overseas Indian Affairs.
